en_954647_0	The Public Relations Unit of the Prime Minister’s Office was opened today.
en_954647_1	The Public Relations Unit was opened under the patronage of Prime Minister Mahinda Rajapaksa at the RA De Mel Mawatha with the presence of Ministers and MPs of the government.
en_954647_2	Addressing the media, Premier Mahinda Rajapksa said the Prime Minister’s Office will be directing the complaints lodged by the public to the relevant government offices.
en_954647_3	The complaints will then be followed up until redress is given.
en_954647_4	Prime Minister Mahinda Rajapksa also mentioned that a convenient atmosphere will be created for the public to directly approach Government Officials.
